    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It\u2019s super smooth to drive and ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
