    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent remains. All interior surfaces, including the high-gloss trim and digital displays, are free of fingerprints or micro-scratching. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced navigation suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history included in the sale. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never driven in inclement weather, and maintained by a non-smoker. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top side. This is a turnkey, collector-grade vehicle that drives with the same precision and tightness as the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
