      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new owner who will appreciate how perfect it is. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
