    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 981-series Cayman S represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated mid-engine engineering. Powered by a 3.4L flat-six, the drivetrain features a 6-speed short-throw manual transmission paired with the Sport Chrono package for precise heel-toe simulation via active rev-matching. The suspension geometry is enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping and a 10mm lower ride height for superior turn-in response. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the variable valve timing (VarioCam Plus), remains in factory-spec order. This example exhibits zero oil seepage, perfect compression across all cylinders, and a pristine undercarriage, making it a true collector-grade specimen.",
